import React from 'react'; import { PubRepo } from '../types'; interface RepoListProps { publicrepos: PubRepo[]; } const RepoList: React.FC = ({ publicrepos }) => { return (
    {publicrepos.slice(0, 5).map((publicrepo) => (

  • {publicrepo.name}

    Full Name: {publicrepo.full_name}

    Private: {publicrepo.private.toString()}

    HTML URL: {publicrepo.html_url}

    Description: {publicrepo.description || 'N/A'}

    Fork: {publicrepo.fork.toString()}

    URL: {publicrepo.url}

    Created At: {publicrepo.created_at}

    Updated At: {publicrepo.updated_at}

    Pushed At: {publicrepo.pushed_at}

    Homepage: {publicrepo.homepage || 'N/A'}

    Size: {publicrepo.size}

    Stargazers Count: {publicrepo.stargazers_count}

    Watchers Count: {publicrepo.watchers_count}

    Language: {publicrepo.language || 'N/A'}

    Has Issues: {publicrepo.has_issues.toString()}

    Has Projects: {publicrepo.has_projects.toString()}

    Has Downloads: {publicrepo.has_downloads.toString()}

    Has Wiki: {publicrepo.has_wiki.toString()}

    Has Pages: {publicrepo.has_pages.toString()}

    Has Discussions: {publicrepo.has_discussions.toString()}

    Forks Count: {publicrepo.forks_count}

    Mirror URL: {publicrepo.mirror_url || 'N/A'}

    Archived: {publicrepo.archived.toString()}

    Disabled: {publicrepo.disabled.toString()}

    Open Issues Count: {publicrepo.open_issues_count}

    License: {publicrepo.license || 'N/A'}

    Web Commit Signoff Required: {publicrepo.web_commit_signoff_required.toString()}

    Topics: {publicrepo.topics.join(', ')}

    Visibility: {publicrepo.visibility}

    Forks: {publicrepo.forks}

    Open Issues: {publicrepo.open_issues}

    Watchers: {publicrepo.watchers}

    Default Branch: {publicrepo.default_branch}

    • ))}
); }; export default RepoList;
